data.description: Spectacular find on a quiet street - close to Blaine Sports complex, restaurants and retail. Plenty of space for all of your hobbies in a large fenced yard, huge garage, and room for equity (exercise or more bedrooms) in an unfinished basement. Enjoy all new appliances, a cozy fireplace, hardwood floors, a kitchen built to entertain and dual master closets. Welcome home.
